descriptionHTML:
Note, this is a watch face for Android Wear

Travel back in time with this 80's retro style 3d StarField effect watch face.
Give your watch face that sci-fi look.
Feel like your traveling through space as stars zip past you, well almost!
Just a fun watch face to take you back in time, nothing fancy, just a simple fun watch face.

Configuration options.
★ Digital / Analogue
★ 12/24 hour
★ Battery
★ Text Color
★ Position the Text, Top Bottom or Centered
★ Multiple Background images to choose from

To install please refer to the Wear Support Page.
https://support.google.com/androidwear/answer/6140435

Is compatible with Android Wear 5+ devices

If you find any bugs, or would like to recommend any modification, please email the developer directly, requests made from within the comments will not be action-ed.
comments: New Update really makes this watch face shine.
Good basic/retro watch face Great start :)
Nice watchface but..... I like the look of the watchface but the Star background skips and the clock is too small (for me). Urbane 2nd Edition
Sweet Great retro digital look, works mint with my Sony watch
recentChanges: Version 18 - Stars are now more rounded and do not look like square when large.
